uote><br />\n<br />\n不如話究竟要還幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由去年做到今年，加埋男友既錢都未還完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8efa03c57f7bb8595328ceeee98269501588e65","tid":191564,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T08:34:20.000Z","msg":"諗起黎姿"}]}